with
    neighbourhoods as (
        select neighbourhood as name, neighbourhood_group, geometry
        from `dbt-cloud-bigquery-450116`.`dataset_22222`.`stg_neighbourhoods`
        order by name
    )

select
    cast(row_number() over (order by name) as int) as neighbourhood_id,
    name,
    english as english_name,
    neighbourhood_group,
    geometry
from neighbourhoods
inner join
    `dbt-cloud-bigquery-450116`.`dataset_22222`.`seed_neighbourhood_english`
    on neighbourhoods.name = seed_neighbourhood_english.chinese

select
    h.host_id,
    h.url,
    h.name,
    h.since,
    h.location,
    h.about,
    h.thumbnail_url,
    h.picture_url,
    d_nbh.neighbourhood_id,
    h.neighbourhood_name
from
    (
        select
            host_id,
            host_url as url,
            host_name as name,
            host_since as since,
            host_location as location,
            host_about as about,
            host_thumbnail_url as thumbnail_url,
            host_picture_url as picture_url,
            host_neighbourhood as neighbourhood_name
        from `dbt-cloud-bigquery-450116`.`dataset_22222`.`stg_listings`
        qualify row_number() over (partition by host_id) = 1
    ) as h
inner join
    `dbt-cloud-bigquery-450116`.`dataset_22222`.`seed_host_neighbourhood_cleansed` as h_nbh_c
    on h.neighbourhood_name = h_nbh_c.host_neighbourhood
inner join
    `dbt-cloud-bigquery-450116`.`dataset_22222`.`dim_neighbourhoods` as d_nbh
    on h_nbh_c.neighbourhood_cleansed = d_nbh.name

                where
